data.description: **** New Paint***New AC Units*** New Carpet***Roof is 3yrs Old*** Pool*** Gorgeous home in Stone Oak that you do not want to miss out on!  This lovely two story home has 5 bedrooms, 4 baths, and 1 half bath.  Vibrant mature trees in the front yard that add a lot of character to the home in addition to the well kept front yard.  Upon entering the home, you'll notice the wood flooring all throughout the interior of the home with the exception of tile located in each of the bathrooms.  Lots of natural light beams through the living area and expand throughout the home as there are many windows on the first floor.  With a wood burning fireplace, kitchen island, wine chiller, and wet bar, you can't go wrong!  The primary bedroom is located downstairs while the remaining bed and baths reside on the second level with a balcony looking out into the backyard in the second primary bedroom.  In ground pool and hot tub located in the backyard with a covered patio and plenty of space for activities and gatherings all year long!
